{"tid":1816480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓出現武漢肺炎疑似病例","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:37:13.000Z","uid":89641,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f77e82c6d3dec1f6274af4bdd3b25f02f921c54f","tid":1816480,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"南韓出現武漢肺炎疑似病例<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報導，南韓出現首例中國武漢肺炎的疑似病例，患者為中國籍36歲女子，去年12月13日至17日曾去過武漢，已被送往首爾國立大學盆唐醫院隔離觀察。<br />\n根據報導，疑似罹患不明肺炎的是一名36歲中國籍婦女，在2019年12月13日至17日旅經武漢，但卻從未進入被認為是感染途徑的海鮮市場、也沒有接觸野生動物等。<br />\n<br />\n目前該病患已送往首爾國立大學盆唐醫院，後續詳細情況仍有待官方釐清。"},{"pid":"0e2885669065fdcfbbda65b7bb67c5d7bd906bbc","tid":1816480,"uid":174206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"中国人本身就係生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc51ba036f8d5f05ba7b61c5d81294bcd5018fe2","tid":1816480,"uid":107422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:22:47.000Z","msg":"Wtf"},{"pid":"105769a589b75b16bb8c1d9a37cd80eb888dee07","tid":1816480,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"MOLA MOLA~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdbc0d3e79568a43c489110466d34bc7eff62be","tid":1816480,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"Wars<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f091518c04705ddb1c2f145edaafb4a532a11ea","tid":1816480,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎<br />\nChina Pneumonia"},{"pid":"561b492d29cb5c9b3af0fd3e0ec5341769b4fd95","tid":1816480,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"應該好快傳晒成個亞洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=